question: Which users follow 'Neo4j'?
cypher:
MATCH (u:User)-[:FOLLOWS]->(me:Me {screen_name: 'neo4j'})
RETURN u.screen_name AS follower
typeql: match $u1 isa user, has screen_name $sn1; $u2 isa user, has screen_name $sn2; (follower: $u1, followed: $u2) isa follows; limit 5; fetch { "follower": $sn1, "followed": $sn2 };

question: List all tweets tagged with the hashtag 'education'.
cypher:
MATCH (t:Tweet)-[:TAGS]->(h:Hashtag {name: 'education'})
RETURN t
typeql: match $t isa tweet, has text $txt; $h isa hashtag, has hashtag_name $hn; (tagged_tweet: $t, tag: $h) isa tags; limit 5; fetch { "tweet": $txt, "hashtag": $hn };

question: Which users are similar to 'Neo4j' with a similarity score above 0.5?
cypher:
MATCH (me:Me {screen_name: 'neo4j'})-[s:SIMILAR_TO]->(u:User)
WHERE s.score > 0.5
RETURN u.screen_name, s.score
typeql: match $u1 isa user, has screen_name $sn1; $u2 isa user, has screen_name $sn2; (source_user: $u1, similar_user: $u2) isa similar_to; limit 5; fetch { "user1": $sn1, "similar": $sn2 };

question: List the top 3 users similar to 'neo4j' by similarity score.
cypher:
MATCH (me:Me {screen_name: 'neo4j'})-[s:SIMILAR_TO]->(u:User)
RETURN u.screen_name AS similar_user, s.score AS similarity
ORDER BY s.score DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $u1 isa user, has screen_name $sn1; $u2 isa user, has screen_name $sn2; (source_user: $u1, similar_user: $u2) isa similar_to; limit 5; fetch { "user1": $sn1, "similar": $sn2 };

question: Which users have retweeted 'neo4j''s tweets the most?
cypher:
MATCH (me:Me {screen_name: 'neo4j'})<-[:MENTIONS]-(tweet:Tweet)<-[:RETWEETS]-(retweet:Tweet)<-[:POSTS]-(retweeter:User)
RETURN retweeter.screen_name AS retweeter, count(*) AS retweets
ORDER BY retweets DESC
LIMIT 10
typeql: match $u isa user, has screen_name $sn; $t isa tweet, has text $txt; (author: $u, content: $t) isa posts; limit 5; fetch { "user": $sn, "tweet": $txt };

question: List the top 5 tweets by 'neo4j' with the most favorites.
cypher:
MATCH (me:Me {screen_name: 'neo4j'})-[:POSTS]->(tweet:Tweet)
RETURN tweet.text, tweet.favorites
ORDER BY tweet.favorites DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $u isa user, has screen_name $sn; $t isa tweet, has text $txt; (author: $u, content: $t) isa posts; limit 5; fetch { "user": $sn, "tweet": $txt };

question: Who are the top 3 users amplified by 'Me'?

MATCH (me:Me)-[:AMPLIFIES]->(u:User)
RETURN u.name, u.screen_name
ORDER BY u.followers DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa me, has screen_name $sn1; $u isa user, has screen_name $sn2; (amplifier: $m, amplified_user: $u) isa amplifies; limit 5; fetch { "amplifier": $sn1, "amplified": $sn2 };

OPTIONAL MATCH (t)<-[:RETWEETS]-(retweet)

MATCH (me:Me {screen_name: 'neo4j'})-[i:INTERACTS_WITH]->(u:User)
RETURN u, count(i) AS interactions
ORDER BY interactions DESC
LIMIT 1
typeql: match $u1 isa user, has screen_name $sn1; $u2 isa user, has screen_name $sn2; (interactor: $u1, target: $u2) isa interacts_with; limit 5; fetch { "user1": $sn1, "user2": $sn2 };
